  "title": "Housekeeping Attendant (Hotel Industry)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Restock room amenities as needed.</li>\n  <li>Deep clean and sanitize guest rooms thoroughly.</li>\n  <li>Report any lost and found items in vacated rooms, as well as any maintenance issues discovered.</li>\n  <li>Respond promptly to guest inquiries.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum 1 year of working experience in a Hotel/ Serviced Apartment</li>\n  <li>Excellent communication </li>\n</ul>\n<p>Interested applicants for the above advertised position(s), please kindly email an updated copy of your resume to: <strong>gs1@talenttradersg.com;</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>EA License No.: 13C6305</p>\n<p>Registration No.: R23117856 CHOE KIN MUN</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>For candidate who applied for the advertised position is deemed to have consented to us that we may collect, use or disclose your personal information for purpose in connection with the services provided by us.</p>",
